    <briefdescription>
<para>Immutable simulation event with (time, sequence) ordering. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para><computeroutput>@dataclass</computeroutput> (order=True) generates <computeroutput>__lt__</computeroutput> from the field declaration order, so <computeroutput>time</computeroutput> is the primary sort key and <computeroutput>sequence</computeroutput> is the FIFO tiebreaker — matching the <computeroutput>CompareTo</computeroutput> logic in the C# <ref refid="classmirror__des_1_1_sim_event" kindref="compound">SimEvent</ref> class. Fields after <computeroutput>sequence</computeroutput> are marked <computeroutput>field</computeroutput>(compare=False) to exclude them from ordering. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
